              \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis year, we\u0026#39;re expecting a bit more than usual from Samsung\u0026#39;s summer Unpacked event. In addition to new clamshell and book-style foldables, rumors say a more affordable Galaxy Z Flip 7 FE and a cutting-edge \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-fold-ultra-wrong-decision/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGalaxy Z Fold Ultra\u003c/a\u003e could join the fun. And on the smartwatch side of things, there should be not two but \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/galaxy-watch-8-full-lineup-renders-reveal/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ethree\u003c/em\u003e new Galaxy Watch models\u003c/a\u003e this time around.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eNow, the Unpacked event itself has gone official, and you can already reserve your new Galaxy gear for a nice bonus.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"ea72-40ac-b5a6a8fae704\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-fold-ultra-wrong-decision/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1081\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Galaxy Z Fold 6 unfolded showing the home screen.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/galaxy-z-fold-6-new-5.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSamsung has sent out invitations to the event, which is now officially scheduled to take place on \u003cstrong\u003eWednesday, July 9 \u003c/strong\u003ein Brooklyn, New York. If you weren\u0026#39;t invited to the in-person show, you can watch it live on \u003ca href=\"https://news.samsung.com/global/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSamsung\u0026#39;s website\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/samsung\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethe company\u0026#39;s YouTube page\u003c/a\u003e. This Unpacked event will kick off at \u003cstrong\u003e10:00 a.m. ET (7:00 a.m. PT)\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n\u003cp\u003eIn the teaser video Samsung sent out with this invite, we see the silhouettes of two stunningly-thin foldables — this aligns with \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/galaxy-z-fold-7-renders-look-stunningly-thin-on-first-glance-but-theres-more-than-meets-the-eye/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eprevious leaks\u003c/a\u003e and a dummy unit that looked \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-7-dummy-phone/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econsiderably thinner than last year\u0026#39;s Fold 6\u003c/a\u003e in a hands-on video.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"6dd2-41be-abd56b3f9dcc\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-7-dummy-phone/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/copy-of-169-17.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                 