                                       \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo-lettermark-11-white.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=420\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo-lettermark-11-white.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=420\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"420\" height=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Samsung\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo-lettermark-11-white.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo-lettermark-11-white.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003e\n                                                                                        \t\n\t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSamsung Galaxy Unpacked\n\t\t\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n                            \n                                                                                                            \u003c/p\u003e\n\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n                            \u003cp\u003eThe wait is almost over — Samsung will unveil its next generation of foldables and smartwatches on July 9th at 10:00 a.m. ET. And starting today, you can reserve a Galaxy Z Flip or Fold 7 to get a $50 Samsung credit, earn triple reward points, and be entered into a $5,000 sweepstakes.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \n            \n            \n\n 